salient setup
make sure boot grub flag turned off and only boot flag on

1. connect to internet
2. sudo reflectuk
3. sudo pacupd
4. sudo pacupg
5. yay -Syu
6. yay -S pamac (3 aur)

search default apps:
file assocs, txt, plain, md to kwrite

in pamac go to prefs and enable third party aur
install nvidia, nvidiautils, nvidiasettings
restart
install egpuswitcher
egpu-switcher config
egpu-switcher setup
restart
pamac updates

hold left click on desktop, change right click to standard menu, middle click for wallpaper

launch feedback to none

screen edges, corner, no action

pamac -S fish
sudo chsh -s /usr/bin/fish
chsh -s `which fish`
restart

add wudgets icons only task manager, thrn edit panel remove normal task manager
change panel to 38px
remove useless pins

pamac
install apps:
    google-chrome
    discord
    vscode/codium
pin apps to taskbar

pamac uninstall firefox

open chrome, dont allow stats, turn on sync and sign in
open discord, sign in, turn off startup in settings
open vscode, go to settings, turn of telemetry, install python and live share extension, install sublime theme

to install spotify:
(last number, change to the key it says failed)
gpg --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys D1742AD60D811D58
then install pamac

